guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">2-week Malaysia Travel Route<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123831\/malaysia-cameron-highlands-salt-in-our-hair.jpg\" alt=\"malaysia cameron highlands salt in our hair\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"malaysia cameron highlands salt in our hair\" class=\"wp-image-19182 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123831\/malaysia-cameron-highlands-salt-in-our-hair.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123831\/malaysia-cameron-highlands-salt-in-our-hair-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123831\/malaysia-cameron-highlands-salt-in-our-hair-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123831\/malaysia-cameron-highlands-salt-in-our-hair-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123831\/malaysia-cameron-highlands-salt-in-our-hair-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123831\/malaysia-cameron-highlands-salt-in-our-hair-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123831\/malaysia-cameron-highlands-salt-in-our-hair-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123831\/malaysia-cameron-highlands-salt-in-our-hair-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123831\/malaysia-cameron-highlands-salt-in-our-hair-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123831\/malaysia-cameron-highlan