-580x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The Jim Thompson Mystery Trail is the most popular of these. Jim Thompson was a well-known businessman who was walking in the Cameron Highlands in the &#x2019;60s when he mysteriously disappeared. He was never found and there are many theories as to what happened. This trail, led by experienced guides, is a great way to learn about its history while discovering some of the spectacular nature.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19155&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123800\/cameron-highlands-malaysia-guide.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123800\/cameron-highlands-malaysia-guide-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123800\/cameron-highlands-malaysia-guide-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Best Things to do in Cameron Highlands, Malaysia\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>You don&#x2019;t need a guide for the mountain trails, however, if you are interested in learning about the impressive local flora and fauna, a guide is essential.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Read about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/malaysia\/penang-georgetown\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Georgetown, Penang<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123807\/cameron-highlands-Jungle-Trail.jpg\" alt=\"cameron highlands Jungle Trail\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"cameron highlands Jungle Trail\" class=\"wp-image-19195 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123807\/cameron-highlands-Jungle-Trail.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123807\/cameron-highlands-Jungle-Trail-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123807\/cameron-highlands-Jungle-Trail-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123807\/cameron-highlands-Jungle-Trail-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.