gs to do&#x2019;, however, the jungle trails and the tea plantations are the only real and natural experiences in the Cameron Highlands. And they are great!<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Flower Farms<\/strong><br>The Cameron Highlands has flower, strawberry, and cactus farms that all want a cut of the tourism boom. We have been explained (and seen ourselves) that the majority of these farms are illegally tapping water from the jungle. This harms the jungle, so we decided not to support these practices and to tell you this important information.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123849\/cameron-highlands-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"cameron highlands malaysia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"377\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cameron highlands malaysia\" class=\"wp-image-19171 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123849\/cameron-highlands-malaysia.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123849\/cameron-highlands-malaysia-300x269.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123849\/cameron-highlands-malaysia-600x538.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123849\/cameron-highlands-malaysia-670x600.jpg 670w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123849\/cameron-highlands-malaysia-904x810.jpg 904w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123849\/cameron-highlands-malaysia-377x338.jpg 377w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123849\/cameron-highlands-malaysia-1536x1376.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\