ril.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip: <\/strong>Check for any Malaysian holidays as it can be crowded during these times.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123803\/best-time-travel-cameron-highlands-malaysia-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"best time travel \"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"313\" alt=\"best time travel \" class=\"wp-image-19201 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123803\/best-time-travel-cameron-highlands-malaysia-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123803\/best-time-travel-cameron-highlands-malaysia-scaled-300x209.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123803\/best-time-travel-cameron-highlands-malaysia-scaled-600x418.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123803\/best-time-travel-cameron-highlands-malaysia-800x557.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123803\/best-time-travel-cameron-highlands-malaysia-1080x752.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123803\/best-time-travel-cameron-highlands-malaysia-450x313.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123803\